{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "ai-services-e2e-nestjs",
		"name": "AI Services - E2E via NestJS Backend",
		"description": "End-to-end testing of AI services through the NestJS apexiq-backend.\n\nFlow:\n1. Run folder '1. Auth' first to get JWT token (auto-saved to variable)\n2. Run folder '2. Onboarding' if new user\n3. Run folder '3. AI - Doubt Resolution' to test AI doubt clearing\n4. Run folder '4. AI - Study Plan' to test AI study plan generation\n\nPre-requisites:\n- NestJS running on port 3000: cd apexiq-backend/apexiq && npm run start:dev\n- Django AI running on port 8000: cd AI_Study && python manage.py runserver 8000\n- PostgreSQL running for NestJS\n- Set variables below before running",
